TASK 1:
       Create a table listing 3 types of printers, 2 types of scanners, and 2 types of webcams, and for each, write one real-life use case (for example: 'Inkjet printer – printing college assignments').


Printers
Inkjet Printer:
               Printing vibrant, high-quality family photos and color-rich school projects at home.

Laser Printer:
              Rapidly printing high volumes of black-and-white text contracts in a busy law office.

3D Printer:
           Creating rapid plastic prototypes of a new product design before manufacturing.

============================

Scanners
Flatbed Scanner:
                Carefully digitizing old, fragile family photographs or delicate artwork without risking damage.

Sheet-fed Scanner: 
                  Quickly scanning large, multi-page stacks of paper invoices to archive them in an accounting department.

============================

Webcams
Integrated (Laptop) Webcam:
                           Attending quick remote team meetings or catching up with friends on a video call while traveling.

Standalone (External) 4K Webcam: 
                                Broadcasting high-definition video for a Twitch live stream or recording a professional online tutorial.

